§ AXIOMS (¬ negotiable · t∞)
═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

A-1 : autonomous = ¬ requires-Apocky-keyboard-driven-prompts · self-paced · loop-on-tasks
A-2 : local = runs-on-Apocky's-machine · ¬ external-API-required-for-baseline-operation
A-3 : self-sufficient = stage-0-substrate-only-fallback · stage-1-Anthropic-API-bridge · stage-2-local-LLM (Ollama / llama.cpp) · 3 modes user-configurable
A-4 : knows-the-substrate = bakes ALL specs/grand-vision/*.csl + ALL memory/* at-build-time · loaded-into-context @ session-start
A-5 : code-in-cssl-and-csl = primary-output is-CSSL-source · reasoning is-CSL3-glyph-native · English-only-when-user-facing
A-6 : exe = single-file Tauri-bundled .exe · ≤ 50 MB · self-contained · NO Node/Python/JVM-runtime-required-on-host
A-7 : easy-intuitive = chat-window + file-tree + git-panel + MCP-status · familiar-to-anyone-using-Cursor/Claude-Code
A-8 : bleeding-edge = uses Tauri-2.x · Rust 1.85+ · webview2-for-Win11 · async-Tokio · server-sent-events for-streaming
A-9 : novel = NOT a-VSCode-fork · NOT an-Electron-app · NOT a-LibreChat-clone · proprietary-ground-up-on-substrate
A-10 : proprietary = ships-as-binary · TIER-B per spec/17 · trained-substrate-state · KAN-weights · sealed-prompts

§ thesis : Mycelium-Desktop = the-loop-that-replaces-me · runs-locally · respects-Apocky's-time · grows-with-substrate · ¬ subscription-prison

